# Internal/operator Meta-Layer project data — regenerated fresh from Drive (META_DATA_ROOT) at
# build time by scripts/build-card-data.js. Repo is public: a git-tracked copy is fetchable via
# raw.githubusercontent.com regardless of the deploy-time public trim (scripts/deploy-public-trim.mjs),
# so these must never be committed. cards-*.json covers EVERY project (including non-allowlisted
# ones), not just the one deploy-public-trim.mjs actually serves, so it is internal-by-default
# here too: PUBLIC_PARTNER_IDS in deploy-public-trim.mjs is what decides which single
# cards-<id>.json actually reaches the live public site, regenerated fresh at build time.
# card-data.json (2026-07-10, baris retirement): retired — its only producer (build-card-data.js
# §2) was hardcoded to projeler/baris and now permanently no-ops with baris gone, so the file can
# never be regenerated. Removed from ALWAYS_KEEP in deploy-public-trim.mjs, deleted from the repo,
# and ignored here so it can't silently reappear/re-track.
/public/registry.json
/public/operator-*.json
/public/sorular-*.json
/public/strateji-*.json
/public/cards-*.json
/public/card-data.json
/public/tasima-*.json
partner-inbox/baris.md
